OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779718268
OL,3,CWest of England's free child travel
OL,4,Cpolicy to be rolled-out across the UK
OL,6,FThe regional policy allows children
OL,7,Fand young people to travel for free on
OL,8,Fbuses during school holidays across
OL,9,FBristol, Bath and North East Somerset,
OL,10,Fand South Gloucestershire. Since
OL,11,Flaunching last year, the scheme has
OL,12,Fseen around 1.4 million free journeys
OL,13,Fmade during the summer, Christmas and
OL,14,FEaster holidays.
OL,16,FThe government has now confirmed it
OL,17,Fwill expand the idea across England
OL,18,Flater this year, with every child aged
OL,19,Fbetween 5 and 15 able to travel for
OL,20,Ffree on participating local bus
OL,21,Fservices throughout August.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
