PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779718268
OL,3,CWest of England's free child travel
OL,4,Cpolicy to be rolled-out across the UK
OL,6,FHelen Godwin welcomed the move and
OL,7,Fsaid the West of England programme had
OL,8,Falready shown clear results.
OL,10,FGodwin said: "There's been a huge
OL,11,Fincrease in public transport use
OL,12,Fthrough our offer already, including
OL,13,Fchildren and families travelling on
OL,14,Four new green buses.
OL,16,F"Bus travel from our lowest income
OL,17,Fareas doubled year-on-year last
OL,18,Fsummer, with kids able to just hop on
OL,19,Fboard and no registration needed.
OL,26,@rD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
