FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779718268
OL,3,CWest of England's free child travel
OL,4,Cpolicy to be rolled-out across the UK
OL,6,F"I'm so excited to see Kids Go Free
OL,7,Freturn again for the school summer
OL,8,Fholidays - helping more children and
OL,9,Fyoung people to explore the best of
OL,10,Fwhat the West has to offer."
OL,12,FTransport Secretary and MP for Swindon
OL,13,FSouth Heidi Alexander, added that the
OL,14,Fgovernment had already seen the impact
OL,15,Fthe policy was having in the region.
OL,26,@rD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
