PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779718268
OL,3,CWest of England's free child travel
OL,4,Cpolicy to be rolled-out across the UK
OL,6,FShe said: "We've already seen what's
OL,7,Fpossible - in the West of England, the
OL,8,FMayor's free travel scheme is making a
OL,9,Freal difference, particularly for
OL,10,Fyoung people in the most deprived
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,F"Free bus travel for every child in
OL,14,FAugust means parents can plan days
OL,15,Fout, visit loved ones and make the
OL,16,Fmost of the holidays without the added
OL,17,Ffinancial pressure."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@MO]uD@AOUyD@TO]
